msg: Based on Adrian's recent comment, committing the changes from OrderReturnServices.xml file. Thanks ofbiz.us team for providing updated patch.
Please do not use the <calculate> element. Mini-language supports UEL:
Also, the <set> element "from-field" attribute has been deprecated, use "from".
Mini-language has an updated schema, it would be best if you configured your XML editor to use it.
